Payoda Inc.





Payoda provides an end-to-end approach to digital marketing that involves a holistic strategy to generate data-driven insights across various channels using cutting-edge tools and technologies.
http://www.payoda.com/campaigns/adobe-analytics


Community Partner





COMPANY INFO





ABOUT
Payoda is a product engineering and services company headquartered in Plano, Texas. Payoda builds world class products, and its digital transformation services helps enterprises transform their business and grow in digital.

Payoda was founded the year 2005 by Anand Purushothaman and Karunya Sampath. Anand has over 15 years of experience in the IT industry, specifically in product design and development and Karunya comes with a strong techno-functional background, bringing over a decade’s experience in business operations and management.


SERVICES OFFERED

Analytics / Business Optimization
Advertizing / Media Buying / Targeting
Campaign Management
Personalization
Search Marketing & Optimization



INDUSTRIES SERVED

Financial Services / Insurance
Healthcare / Pharma / Biotech / Life Sci
